snippet.title: Tapu Sena ने कर दिया Parents को परेशान! | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Bhide V/s Tapu Sena
snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to LIV Comedy: 
https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBIT1FSJW6yTlzqK-31FDWg?sub_confirmation=1

Komal gets angry with Goli and asks him to end the strike, but is shocked by his behavior. Bhide takes out Tapu's frustration on Sonu. Jethalal wants to share the problem with his best friend Taarak Mehta. Champaklal goes to school with them. He tries to explain to Tapu and the other children the unfairness of their demands. Are you listening to Tapu Champaklal?

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 65
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #tmkoc #comedy2024 #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #comedy #jethalal #tarakmehta 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Click here to watch more episodes from 'Bhide V/s Tapu Sena' : https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSBrJc2CLaW5IzUPoMSw-12

snippet.description:
Today I will be making a Gaming Room Setup inside a Train!         

Also get ready to power up and #GameWithoutCompromise with the Lenovo LOQ powered by Intel® Core™ Processors (14th Gen). Game, stream, create, and multitask your way through seamlessly! Play hard, work smart, and become the gaming legend you have always wanted to be!    

Click on the link and check out this amazing laptop: https://lnv.gy/3XuqYnP     

Also all the Star Wars Fans!! The force is totally with you, Jedi
With every purchase of Intel Core 14th gen HX gaming laptop from Amazon or Flipkart you get STAR WARS OUTLAWS for FREEEE, which is usually available in the market for about INR 6,000*. This offer ends July 31, 2024, only available on Amazon.in and Flipkart.

In Today's video I travel in Bharat ki Shaan Rajdhani and I make a Gaming Room inside it! I make my Gaming setup using Gaming gadgets and some decoration items which I put up lightly without any damage. I use Gaming steering wheel, Minecraft Items, Gaming Controllers, Mouse, Keyboards. We also show the Good Aspects of Indian Railways which is actually amazing. Loved the Toilets 10/10. Good Job Indian Railways! The food was also amazing! Our today's goal is to eat Chole Bhature in Delhi and we travel in Train while playing games.
I am #Mythpat and being a #Gaming Youtuber I think this is the best way to promote and encourage audience to use Indian Railways. This video is made to show to positive aspects of our amazing Indian Railways! Hope you enjoy this #vlog in Hindi with my Wife @urmilaaa

snippet.title: Tauba Tauba | Bad Newz | Vicky Kaushal | Triptii Dimri | Karan Aujla | In cinemas 19th July
snippet.description:
Experience the magic of Karan Aujla, Triptii Dimri and Vicky Kaushal's first-ever collaboration in "Tauba Tauba" from Bad Newz! This high-energy dance number is guaranteed to make you move. Get ready to dance like never before!

👉 Subscribe to Saregama Music: https://bit.ly/3FkAS0W

Credits:
Composer - Karan Aujla
Singer - Karan Aujla
Lyricist - Karan Aujla
Music Producer - Yeah Proof
Special Thanks Azeem Dayani
Mixing And Mastering - Hanish Taneja
Choreographer - Bosco- Ceaser
Song Editor- Adele Jerome Pereira
Production Designer- Manini Mishra
DOP- Santhana Krishnan Ravichandran
Costume Designer- Samidha Wangnoo

Bad Newz in cinemas 19th July.

Amazon Prime presents
In association with Dharma Productions and Leo Media Collective
A Leo Media Collective production
BAD NEWZ
Starring Vicky Kaushal, Triptii Dimri and Ammy Virk
Directed by Anand Tiwari
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar, Apoorva Mehta, Amritpal Singh Bindra & Anand Tiwari
Written by Ishita Moitra & Tarun Dudeja

Lyrics:

Husn tera tauba tauba X 4
Oh le liya ladki ne dil humara,
Abhi thoda saaf nahi lag raha irada,
Choti bahaut lambi nahi rakhi hai mutiyar ne,
Haaye dikhta nahi hai parranda, dikhta hai Prada,
Figure se lagti Latino
Ek baar batado itni kyun ho shaukinon,
Kal hi tum Italy se aayi hai marjaaniye, aur purse tenu Paris se mangvaya hai Valentino
Haan tujhe kyun na dekhu, tujhse kya seekhu, tujh mein kya likhu?

Husn tera tauba tauba X 4

Hum hai malana aur who kief,
Aira-gaira dekhti nahi waise toh shareef hoon, yahaan par kehti hai too much desi hai,
isliye chill kare London aur party at Ibiza hai, humaare liye bilkul bhee free nahi lagti, IG
story pe toh Bora Bora , awaaz tumhari sohniye surilee noori ke (Old Punjabi singer) jaise
lagti, jab kamar hile “Nora” lagti,
Milna dass de (bata de), tha (jagah) dass de, meri jaan dass de (bata de),

Husn tera tauba tauba X 4

Haaye! Mitron se aankh tumhari maange kangna (mujhse tumhari aankh Kangana maang
rahi hai),
Abhi main banwa dunga mujhe bata toh sahi,
Jaan maang lo main tujhpe jaan waar (jaan nyochavar karna) du, khud nikal jaayegi tu
hass toh sahi, tujhmein nasha pehli tod (daaru) jaisa hai kude (girl), sohniye daru ka toh
naam lagta hai, hum se zyaada tumhari popularity ho gayi hai, tum bahar nikli toh sadko
par jam (traffic jam) lagta hai,
Haa... baat maan meri, mehman meri, tum ho jaan meri,

Husn tera tauba tauba X 4

Jaan Nisar Episode 29 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Danish Taimoor - Hiba Bukhari - Haroon Shahid - 7th July 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

snippet.description: Bajaj CNG motorcycle - Freedom 125 - has finally gone on sale in India at a starting price of Rs 95,000 whereas the top-end Disc brake + LED light version costs Rs 1.10 lacs (ex-showroom). What makes it unique is the fact that it gets a 2KG CNG tank beneath the seat and a 2-litre petrol fuel tank. cumulatively, both offer a range of 330Km (realistic range). On CNG alone, it offers over 108kmpl thus making it the most fuel efficient motorcycle on sale in India right now. Hope you enjoy this video.

snippet.title: From PM Modi To Manipur MP, Here Are The Most Controversial Speeches Of the 18th Lok Sabha
snippet.description:
Parliament Speech: As the 18th Lok Sabha session concludes, we revisit some of the most controversial speeches made by prominent leaders. From Prime Minister Modi's striking remarks to Rahul Gandhi's fiery rebuttals, and Mahua Moitra's bold statements to Anurag Thakur's vehement arguments, each speech left a significant mark on the parliamentary proceedings. The sessions also featured impassioned speeches by Bimol Akoijam on regional issues, Asaduddin Owaisi's critiques of government policies, and Harsimrat Kaur Badal's pointed accusations. This compilation captures the intensity and drama that defined this session.

Yahan to bhare samp kare baat jaise bane pac, 
reefer with tequila, kare bandiyon ko gheela,

25 show kare sold out,
Mujhse Poocho mat Haal, pure Saal ekatha Karoo Jake maal lage Jaise koi Godown 

Wow now, slow down,
Gaane inke sune mai So raha hoo, 
Ye rappers hai joke inse poochoge toh,
honge He/He inke pronoun,

Ye jaante hai log that Im killing, killing it,
Inse poochoge toh they be fearing my pen again,
So cold, aise lage, they be feeling the chill again,
Mera flow lage gold, it be gleaming so elegant 

Rapping fast ab, masterclass du inko
Stacking racks up, pass the cash ab ginlo
Acting whack, you lack the facts, the info 
Album scrapped, doo back to back ab single

Ignore karoo mene to na Hi bola 
Hoti inki chandi par ye to buss chahye sona, 
Mic to la, foes I caught-many jaise ayatollah, 
Sade pade kyun ho beta khade khade Vibe lo na 

Lagoo thoda bi-polar, abhi bhi na mic choda
Peeke dhai tola, kabhi kabhi lagoo high thoda, 
side ho ja, tere gaano se na koi hype ho ra
Sung a lullaby, bye bye ab to bhai so raha
-
Ye de re mujhe apna opinion 
Me boloo abe chup be Saale
Mujhse nahi chahiye teri rai,
Kara mat ghutne kaale, 
Ye launde bane Bawarchi
Apni baaton se ye khoob paka re
Ye aake kyun bhok rahe idhar 
Mene na kutte pale,

Inhe bolo they not ready, 
Aisa na hota ki meri aim not steady 
Agar chahiye war then ofcourse they gon get it 
interview bhi na chale bina
Name drop kare 

I’m sick of it, internet bickering, 
Baton ki na fikar, bitches sitting there giggling
click a pen, doge mujhe Dhaka then I just go and Kill again 
Cashflow krish with the big dick jiggling 

Not a joke though, kare choke wo, 
Mix the B in the pot with the coco,
Mere sab dost - sare cutthroat,
Bolo sabko I don’t give a fuck though 

kar believe I need to keep it hundo,
Khalbali ki kal Umeed hai humko 
Verbally yahan har gali me jung ho 
Chad bali, yahan hadbadi me mar lo,

Le gaye hum kudsi bawe
Garmi me kardoo me Sardi yahan dekh,
Kisi bhi sheher me ho kuch bhi kalesh, 
I Walk with my chest out - Urfi Javed

You don’t know jack, ye beat pe tochen
She been stalking me jaise fee fi of fum,
A giant in the game, you’ll just reach my scrotum,
She can get the pole, I mean the totem

Jaan Nisar Episode 27 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints - Danish Taimoor - Hiba Bukhari - Haroon Shahid - 5th July 2024 - Har Pal Geo

Jaan Nisar Digitally Presented by Happilac Paints

7th Sky Entertainment’s mega project, Jaan Nisar, is the most awaited drama serial of the year.
The highly anticipated project marks the return of the successful on-screen couple of Danish Taimoor and Hiba Bukhari in an unforgettable love story that will steal your heart.

Nosherwan Ghaznavi, a wealthy young man, faces a pivotal moment in his life after his brother's death. This tragedy burdens Nosherwan Ghaznavi with numerous responsibilities, which he reluctantly accepts, only to find them later proving detrimental. However, his life takes a transformative turn upon meeting Dua, falling in love with her at first sight, but it places him at a critical juncture with his responsibilities.

Dua, a beautiful girl from a humble background, is raised by her parents alongside her two sisters. Despite her innocence, fate subjects Dua to a string of misfortunes before encountering Nosherwan Ghaznavi. However, their meeting completely changes their lives.

Will Nowsherwan Ghaznavi find love? What challenges will he face in balancing his duties and his love for Dua? Will his responsibilities jeopardize his love for Dua? What past events have shaped Dua's life, and will they resurface to trouble her? Will Dua return Nowsherwan Ghaznavi’s love?

snippet.title: How We Built a VILLAGE in This EMPTY Minecraft World!
snippet.description:
𝗔𝗽𝗽𝗹𝗶𝗰𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻:
https://bit.ly/4coUX5p

Well, did you hear?𝗡𝗲𝘄𝘁𝗼𝗻 𝘀𝗰𝗵𝗼𝗼𝗹 𝗼𝗳 𝘁𝗲𝗰𝗵𝗻𝗼𝗹𝗼𝗴𝘆 𝗵𝗮𝘀 𝗯𝗿𝗼𝘂𝗴𝗵𝘁 𝘆𝗼𝘂 𝘀𝗼𝗺𝗲𝘁𝗵𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗴𝗿𝗼𝘂𝗻𝗱𝗯𝗿𝗲𝗮𝗸𝗶𝗻𝗴–  𝗶𝗻𝗱𝗶𝗮’𝘀 𝗳𝗶𝗿𝘀𝘁 𝗴𝗹𝗼𝗯𝗮𝗹 𝗯.𝘁𝗲𝗰𝗵 𝗗𝗲𝗴𝗿𝗲𝗲 𝗣𝗿𝗼𝗴𝗿𝗮𝗺 𝗶𝗻 𝗖𝗼𝗺𝗽𝘂𝘁𝗲𝗿 𝗦𝗰𝗶𝗲𝗻𝗰𝗲 𝗮𝗻𝗱 𝗔𝗜

And guess what?𝗔𝗱𝗺𝗶𝘀𝘀𝗶𝗼𝗻𝘀 𝗮𝗿𝗲 𝗻𝗼𝘄 𝗼𝗽𝗲𝗻! You can kickstart your journey by appearing for the 𝗡𝗦𝗔𝗧 𝗘𝘅𝗮𝗺 𝗼𝗻 𝗝𝘂ly. This is there last phase, so do register now. 

Visit Newton School of Technology’s website for all the deets and to register for the exam.
𝗪𝗲𝘀𝗯𝗶𝘁𝗲:
https://bit.ly/4bu9cV8

Trust me, this is your chance to turn your coding dreams into reality! 𝗙𝗿𝗼𝗺 𝗱𝗼𝗺𝗶𝗻𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗶𝗻𝘁𝗲𝗿𝗻𝗮𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻𝗮𝗹 𝗰𝗼𝗱𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝗰𝗼𝗺𝗽𝗲𝘁𝗶𝘁𝗶𝗼𝗻𝘀 𝘁𝗼 𝗹𝗮𝘂𝗻𝗰𝗵𝗶𝗻𝗴 𝘆𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗼𝘄𝗻 𝘀𝘁𝗮𝗿𝘁𝘂𝗽, 𝗡𝗲𝘄𝘁𝗼𝗻 𝗦𝗰𝗵𝗼𝗼𝗹 𝗼𝗳 𝗧𝗲𝗰𝗵𝗻𝗼𝗹𝗼𝗴𝘆 𝗵𝗮𝘀 𝗴𝗼𝘁 𝘆𝗼𝘂𝗿 𝗯𝗮𝗰𝗸 𝗲𝘃𝗲𝗿𝘆 𝘀𝘁𝗲𝗽 𝗼𝗳 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝘄𝗮𝘆 𝘁𝗼 𝗯𝗲𝗰𝗼𝗺𝗲 𝘁𝗵𝗲 𝘁𝗼𝗽 𝟭%.


We Transformed This Empty Bedrock World into a Working Village...

snippet.title: VEG vs. NON VEG. | Who is STRONGER & will LIVE MORE?
snippet.description:
Best Sunscreen for Oily Skin - https://bit.ly/4eVoiGi 

Who are more powerful, smarter, intelligent, active, and live longer: vegetarians or non-vegetarians? Just as a cow eats grass and a lion eats meat, similarly, what is human biology naturally designed for eating? Fruits and vegetables, or animal meat? Because our natural food will give us a fit and long life.
Let's settle the debate that has been going on for years once and for all today, because today the referee of this wrestling match will be SCIENCE itself, whose sole purpose is to know the truth! And honestly speaking, it needs to be settled because nowadays many people are adopting extreme diets influenced by their favorite influencers on social media, based on half information, which is even risking their lives.

Indian moms dealing with holiday homework given by school teachers during summer break , Family trips , horse ridding , trekking , hiking . watching sunsets , sunrise at famous hill tops , creating memories clicking pictures , tourist locations and rush of people and traffic jams , mother excited to go vacation getting her beauty regime by parlour didi , waxing , facial , threading , bleach , dtan , shopping from sarojini nagar to travel , buying gifts for relatives on vacay , travelling by train enjoying , singing eating train food , road trip with family , stopping at dhaba , mom feeding her home cooked food puri aloo jeera sabzi , middle class dad driving on highway , kids singing fighting taking pictures on the way to himachal and so much more ..
This video is filled with such memories and situations we all have been in. 

Relish and Relive your Childhood Memories.. You will have major nostalgia

snippet.title: Team India meets Prime Minister Narendra Modi
snippet.description:
The T20 World Cup-winning Indian cricket team landed in Delhi on July 4 aboard a specially-arranged charter flight, five days after winning the coveted title in Barbados where it was stranded due to a category 4 hurricane.

The team met Prime Minister Narendra Modi before leaving for Mumbai where a victory parade is scheduled for the T20 World Cup champions at 5 p.m.

The Indian team will be celebrating the win at The Wankhede Stadium in mumbai later today. The stadium will be open to general public as well.

The gates will close at 6 p.m. or when the stands are filled to capacity, whichever is earlier.

For live updates on Team India arrival click here: https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/team-india-arrival-live-updates-july-4/article68365597.ece

snippet.title: Mahua Moitra Returns To Lok Sabha With Fiery Speech, Corners Modi Govt On Manipur, Kashmir & Ayodhya
snippet.description:
TMC Lok Sabha MP Mahua Moitra made her comeback speech while replying to the motion of thanks to the President's address. Notably, the TMC MP was suspended from Lok Sabha just months from elections over cash-for-query allegations. Mahua denied any wrongdoing. And in her comeback speech, she came down heavily on BJP and the Modi government. In her more than half-an-hour-long speech, Mahua cornered BJP over Manipur violence, Kashmir, Ayodhya and many more issues.
